title: Coastal Landscape
description: A scenic view of a coastal landscape featuring a lush green hillside meeting the water. The shoreline is partially sandy with rocky outcrops, and the calm waters reflect the surrounding greenery. In the distance, there are hints of boats and more land, creating a tranquil and natural atmosphere.

title: Scenic River Valley
description: A panoramic view of a lush green valley with rolling hills and a winding river. The landscape is vibrant with trees and fields, under a clear blue sky, showcasing the beauty of nature.

title: Cross-Section of a Landscape
description: The image depicts a cross-section of a landscape showing the surface and underground features. The top half illustrates grassy areas with rocks and a small river flowing through. The bottom half reveals a network of caves and underground water bodies, highlighting the geological structure beneath the surface.

title: Mountain Landscape with Vegetation
description: An aerial view of a mountainous area featuring a mix of rocky terrain and dense green forest. The image shows a slope with a noticeable rockslide area, where the earth has shifted, exposing bare rock amidst the surrounding trees.
